title: Thirsty Seconds | NTSP

description:
Saturday: We’ll be hosting an aid station for the Deception Pass 50k. See Slack for volunteering details.

Saturday night: Free & sheltered camping with a fire at Raymond’s family farm near Burlington (thanks Raymond!). See Slack for camping details.

Sunday: Meet at North Chuckanut TH Sunday morning for several route options exploring the Chuckanut area. Social post-run at GRUFF brewing. For all the routes be prepared with navigation!

The longest route runs ends at GRUFF Brewing! Please coordinate carpooling if wanting this option! Bring your ID since no minors are allowed at GRUFF brewing.
